    {
      "id": "stage-01",
      "order": 1,
      "title": "Definición y medición",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Definición y medición de ángulos</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr)); gap: 14px; }\n    .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; }\n    svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display:block; margin: 8px auto; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Definición y medición de ángulos</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.º grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Geometría</span></p>\n\n  <h2>¿Qué es un ángulo?</h2>\n  <p>Un <strong>ángulo</strong> es la abertura formada por dos <strong>semirrectas</strong> (rayos) que comparten un mismo punto de origen llamado <strong>vértice</strong>.</p>\n\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 160\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"220\" height=\"160\">\n    <!-- Rayo 1 horizontal -->\n    <line x1=\"40\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"200\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n    <!-- Rayo 2 inclinado -->\n    <line x1=\"40\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"20\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n    <!-- Arco del ángulo -->\n    <path d=\"M 80,120 A 40,40 0 0,0 68,88\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <!-- Vértice -->\n    <circle cx=\"40\" cy=\"120\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n    <!-- Etiquetas -->\n    <text x=\"28\" y=\"140\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#f97316\" font-weight=\"bold\">V</text>\n    <text x=\"85\" y=\"100\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#e11d48\">α</text>\n    <text x=\"190\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#4f46e5\">semirrecta</text>\n    <text x=\"145\" y=\"18\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#4f46e5\">semirrecta</text>\n  </svg>\n\n  <h2>¿Cómo se miden los ángulos?</h2>\n  <p>Los ángulos se miden en <strong>grados</strong> (símbolo: <strong>°</strong>) usando un instrumento llamado <strong>transportador</strong>.</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Una vuelta completa equivale a $360°$.</li>\n    <li>Media vuelta equivale a $180°$.</li>\n    <li>Un cuarto de vuelta equivale a $90°$.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <div class=\"tip\">\n    <strong>Pasos para medir un ángulo con el transportador:</strong>\n    <ol>\n      <li>Coloca el centro del transportador sobre el <strong>vértice</strong> del ángulo.</li>\n      <li>Alinea la línea base del transportador con uno de los lados del ángulo.</li>\n      <li>Lee la medida donde el otro lado cruza la escala del transportador.</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Recuerda:</strong> Los ángulos se nombran con letras griegas ($\\alpha$, $\\beta$, $\\gamma$) o con tres letras mayúsculas, donde la del medio es el vértice. Por ejemplo: $\\angle ABC$.\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": ["360°", "180°", "90°", "\\angle ABC"],
      "assets": []
    },
    {
      "id": "stage-02",
      "order": 2,
      "title": "Clasificación de ángulos",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Clasificación de ángulos</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr)); gap: 14px; }\n    .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; text-align:center; }\n    .card p { margin: 0.3rem 0; }\n    .card .label { font-weight: 700; color: #4338ca; }\n    .card .desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555; }\n    svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display:block; margin: 8px auto; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Clasificación de ángulos</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.º grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Geometría</span></p>\n\n  <p>Los ángulos se clasifican según su <strong>medida</strong>:</p>\n\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    <!-- Ángulo agudo -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"130\" height=\"110\">\n        <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"130\" y2=\"100\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"90\" y2=\"20\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <path d=\"M 55,100 A 35,35 0 0,0 47,75\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n        <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"100\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n        <text x=\"52\" y=\"92\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\">45°</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Ángulo agudo</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Mide menos de $90°$</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Ángulo recto -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"130\" height=\"110\">\n        <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"130\" y2=\"100\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <rect x=\"20\" y=\"80\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" />\n        <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"100\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n        <text x=\"45\" y=\"78\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\">90°</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Ángulo recto</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Mide exactamente $90°$</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Ángulo obtuso -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"110\">\n        <line x1=\"30\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"100\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"30\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"15\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <path d=\"M 65,100 A 35,35 0 0,0 33,68\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n        <circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"100\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n        <text x=\"50\" y=\"82\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\">130°</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Ángulo obtuso</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Mide más de $90°$ y menos de $180°$</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Ángulo llano -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 80\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"75\">\n        <line x1=\"10\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"50\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <path d=\"M 110,50 A 30,30 0 0,0 50,50\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n        <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"50\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n        <text x=\"72\" y=\"35\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\">180°</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Ángulo llano</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Mide exactamente $180°$</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Ángulo completo -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"130\" height=\"110\">\n        <line x1=\"30\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"130\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"70\" r=\"35\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n        <circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"70\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n        <text x=\"22\" y=\"30\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\">360°</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Ángulo completo</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Mide exactamente $360°$</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Resumen</h2>\n  <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; margin:1rem 0;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background:#eef2ff;\">\n        <th style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center; color:#3730a3;\">Tipo</th>\n        <th style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center; color:#3730a3;\">Medida</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">Agudo</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">$0° &lt; \\alpha &lt; 90°$</td></tr>\n      <tr style=\"background:#f9fafb;\"><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">Recto</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">$\\alpha = 90°$</td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">Obtuso</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">$90° &lt; \\alpha &lt; 180°$</td></tr>\n      <tr style=\"background:#f9fafb;\"><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">Llano</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">$\\alpha = 180°$</td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">Completo</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #d1d5db; padding:0.5rem; text-align:center;\">$\\alpha = 360°$</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Recuerda:</strong> El ángulo recto se indica con un pequeño cuadrado en el vértice. Es uno de los ángulos más importantes en geometría.\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": ["0° < \\alpha < 90°", "\\alpha = 90°", "90° < \\alpha < 180°", "\\alpha = 180°", "\\alpha = 360°"],
      "assets": []
    },
    {
      "id": "stage-03",
      "order": 3,
      "title": "Ángulos según su posición",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Ángulos según su posición</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr)); gap: 14px; }\n    .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; }\n    svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display:block; margin: 8px auto; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Ángulos según su posición</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.º grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Geometría</span></p>\n\n  <h2>Ángulos complementarios</h2>\n  <p>Dos ángulos son <strong>complementarios</strong> cuando sus medidas <strong>suman 90°</strong>.</p>\n  $$\\alpha + \\beta = 90°$$\n\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 150\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\">\n    <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"130\" x2=\"180\" y2=\"130\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"130\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"20\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"130\" x2=\"140\" y2=\"50\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\" />\n    <rect x=\"20\" y=\"110\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#999\" stroke-width=\"1\" />\n    <path d=\"M 60,130 A 40,40 0 0,0 52,100\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <path d=\"M 48,103 A 36,36 0 0,0 20,90\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <text x=\"55\" y=\"118\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#e11d48\">α = 60°</text>\n    <text x=\"28\" y=\"95\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#16a34a\">β = 30°</text>\n    <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"130\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n  </svg>\n\n  <div class=\"example\">\n    <h4>Ejemplo</h4>\n    <p>Si $\\alpha = 35°$, ¿cuánto mide su complemento?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">$\\beta = 90° - 35° = 55°$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Ángulos suplementarios</h2>\n  <p>Dos ángulos son <strong>suplementarios</strong> cuando sus medidas <strong>suman 180°</strong>.</p>\n  $$\\alpha + \\beta = 180°$$\n\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 240 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"240\" height=\"100\">\n    <line x1=\"10\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"230\" y2=\"80\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <line x1=\"120\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"15\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\" />\n    <path d=\"M 85,80 A 35,35 0 0,0 87,52\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <path d=\"M 155,80 A 35,35 0 0,1 87,52\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <text x=\"75\" y=\"70\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\">α=50°</text>\n    <text x=\"130\" y=\"60\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#16a34a\">β=130°</text>\n    <circle cx=\"120\" cy=\"80\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n  </svg>\n\n  <div class=\"example\">\n    <h4>Ejemplo</h4>\n    <p>Si $\\alpha = 115°$, ¿cuánto mide su suplemento?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">$\\beta = 180° - 115° = 65°$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Ángulos adyacentes</h2>\n  <p>Dos ángulos son <strong>adyacentes</strong> cuando comparten un lado y el vértice, y no se superponen. Los ángulos suplementarios que comparten un lado son un caso especial de ángulos adyacentes.</p>\n\n  <h2>Ángulos opuestos por el vértice</h2>\n  <p>Cuando dos rectas se cruzan, se forman cuatro ángulos. Los ángulos que están en posiciones opuestas son <strong>iguales</strong>.</p>\n\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 160\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"220\" height=\"160\">\n    <line x1=\"10\" y1=\"130\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"30\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <line x1=\"10\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"110\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2\" />\n    <path d=\"M 135,80 A 25,25 0 0,1 118,60\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n    <path d=\"M 85,80 A 25,25 0 0,1 102,100\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n    <path d=\"M 118,60 A 25,25 0 0,1 85,80\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n    <path d=\"M 102,100 A 25,25 0 0,1 135,80\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n    <text x=\"140\" y=\"68\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\" font-weight=\"bold\">α</text>\n    <text x=\"68\" y=\"98\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\" font-weight=\"bold\">α</text>\n    <text x=\"85\" y=\"62\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#16a34a\" font-weight=\"bold\">β</text>\n    <text x=\"122\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#16a34a\" font-weight=\"bold\">β</text>\n    <circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"80\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#f97316\" />\n  </svg>\n\n  <div class=\"tip\">\n    <strong>Propiedad:</strong> Los ángulos opuestos por el vértice son siempre iguales: $\\alpha = \\alpha'$ y $\\beta = \\beta'$.\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Ejercicios</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Calcula el ángulo que falta:</h4>\n    <p class=\"step\">1. Dos ángulos complementarios: $\\alpha = 42°$. ¿Cuánto mide $\\beta$? ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">2. Dos ángulos suplementarios: $\\alpha = 78°$. ¿Cuánto mide $\\beta$? ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">3. Dos rectas se cruzan formando un ángulo de $65°$. ¿Cuánto mide el ángulo opuesto? ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">4. Dos rectas se cruzan formando un ángulo de $65°$. ¿Cuánto mide cada ángulo adyacente? ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">5. Un ángulo y su complementario miden lo mismo. ¿Cuánto mide cada uno? ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Respuestas:</strong> 1) $\\beta = 48°$ · 2) $\\beta = 102°$ · 3) $65°$ · 4) $115°$ · 5) $45°$ cada uno.\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": ["\\alpha + \\beta = 90°", "\\alpha + \\beta = 180°"],
      "assets": []
    }
  ]
}
